text: "Doctor, My Eyes" is a 1972 debut single from Jackson Browne. It is the first single from his debut studio album Jackson Browne and went to number 8 in the United States and number 4 in Canada. It was covered by The Jackson 5 for their sixth studio album Lookin' Through the Windows in 1972. ==References== Category:1972 songs Category:Debut singles Category:Soft rock songs Category:Jackson Browne songs Category:The Jackson 5 songs
title: Doctor, My Eyes
